tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
context: Pre and Post Delivery Care,menopause advice,
review: From a very long time I was looking for a good gynecologist with whom I could share my problems without any hesitation.. and I was very happy to find Dr Nikita who is amazing and explains our problems and what needs to be done... I had breasts pain and in less time she gave me appointment and checked me and made my pain relief... I am very happy.. I have already started to suggest to many of friends and family members to see her ** *** ** *** *****

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Value for money,
review: Dr. Nikitha Murthy explained everything very neatly.  We are happy continue treatment with her.  Staff is very friendly.

With Dr Nikitha Murthy i had very good experience *** ** * **** **** ** .She diagnosis exact cause and give the treatment according to the cause.She explains in detail. I recommend her to all the women who wants to conceive. I give her five star.
She is good and provide her valuable suggestions and traeted as friendly. It will help us to improve the confidence.
Dr Nikitha is very understanding, kind and friendly. Had a wonderful experience. She takes time and diagonisis clearly. Appreciate her patience from the start!! Would highly recommend...
reply_text: Thank you so much for your feedback

review: Went to Sukhi health clinic for my infertility problem.. Doctor was very polite and explained whats the problem and what need to be done step by step and always gave the best option to consider. I strongly recommend Dr. Nikitha for all gynecological and infertility related problem.
reply_text: Thank you so much! Hope your journey towards pregnancy is short but successful. Take care.

review: Dr. Nikitha has been extremely helpful and patient. She provides comfort and gives every individual opportunity to express their issues and findes resolution. Fertility is a difficult topic but she ensured transparency and suggested options available. Her guidance , help support is unparalleled.

********** ****** ** * **** **** ****** * **** *** ** ** **** ****** ******* *** *** ***** ** ****** ******* ******* She is very responsible, trustworthy and cooperative thanks u so much Doctor 
I recommend dr nikitha who has gyno related problems should visit to her
She talks very friendly.... her positive reaction will definitely cure your health problems....
Thank you mam
reply_text: Thank you dear. Happy to help!
